Package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.util.vector

Record Class Vector3Dd

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.util.vector.Vector3Dd
All Implemented Interfaces:
IVector3D
public record Vector3Dd(double x, double y, double z) extends Record implements IVector3D
Represents a double x/y/z set.

This class is thread-safe, as all modifications return a new instance.

Author:
Pim
